text: You are the merely dust on the shoe of anyone, all ignore none wish to speak to man who relies on a greater power to survive.
You have lost your former glory, you are now seen a mere frog in a well.
You are almost on your last legs, while your army may continue to push, your appearance to the world is only that of a rat.
You are known to the world, but do not become the snake who tries to consume the elephant.
You fame increases, your courtesy intimidates of a tiger, which you murdered.
Your decisions are made up by yourself, but your will is not of your own.
You have made it to the top, as you were all along, a hawk who hid his talons.
